\n到我高中之後，佢兩個成日鬧交<br />\n然後後尾我發現老豆出面又有個女人（三任）<br />\n個女人仲要我細過見過<br />\n（果時老豆話個女人係佢家姐，我𡃁仔當然深信不疑<br />\n最後老豆同二任離左婚<br />\n搬左出去同個三任住<br />\n<br />\n呢家我仍然同二任阿媽住<br />\n不過對老豆經麻木了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 仲有同一二三任見面食飯"},{"pid":"b59d55e64f1af52cb4a13f6597f824a52d662a0a","tid":294022,"uid":124602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T04:05:20.000Z","msg":"為左呢個topic開account<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為同身邊既人講 根本無人明<br />\n<br />\n老母唔肯接受現實<br />\n選擇去相信個仆街既大話<br />\n<br />\n因為經濟能力未許可走唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n身邊啲長輩成日話我令我老母難做兼難受<br />\n誰人曾照顧過我的感受"},{"pid":"7e28e396cbe40fbccfe0fd30ea6a2015559b8dee","tid":294022,"uid":59192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T04:43:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我個情況係<br />\n<br />\n老豆同老母奉子成婚，即係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後佢地係我細個幾歲既時候離婚<br />\n之後掉低我比阿公阿婆湊大<br />\n大概我小四既時候老豆接返我同佢住<br />\n然後果時佢同緊個女人（二任）同居<br />\n之後結埋婚 我就同老豆加第二任阿媽一齊住<br />\n<br />\n到我高中之後，佢兩個成日鬧交<br />\n然後後尾我發現老豆出面又有個女人（三任）<br />\n個女人仲要我細過見過<br />\n（果時老豆話個女人係佢家姐，我𡃁仔當然深信不疑<br />\n最後老豆同二任離左婚<br />\n搬左出去同個三任住<br />\n<br />\n呢家我仍然同二任阿媽住<br />\n不過對老豆經麻木了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 仲有同一二三任見面食飯</blockquote><br />\n你老豆好有錢?"},{"pid":"86891621cdf86195497a1e9af9b3a3e6532d542b","tid":294022,"uid":104194,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T08:33:24.000Z","msg":"好老實講 我老豆睇a片+打飛機<br />\n我都覺好難面對佢"},{"pid":"51667f2f99501c9bf5c1406cf904dcca55a4a716","tid":294022,"uid":42879,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T08:39:56.000Z","msg":"原諒唔到，點解當年佢唔包多幾個返深圳買多幾層樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n身邊好多人都係因為老竇包二奶發左達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc8ba911d1d9634d9e796c8e46b56a0ef2057d21","tid":294022,"uid":110840,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T08:56:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cebe0f55ee3cc4d8263d5acfba0cdbf3a21b9328","tid":294022,"uid":46347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T09:09:08.000Z","msg":"離少少題<br />\n<br />\n老豆係以前做中港司機 一星期有幾晚番唔到黎<br />\n但番到黎真係對我地好好 (任何方面)<br />\n同正常溫馨家庭冇分別<br />\n<br />\n如果你知佢有二奶 你會點？"},{"pid":"dc57b28818f70583755f5f8bab1b0d1962944fb5","tid":294022,"uid":24596,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T09:22:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講真人地兩老嘅感情事，關你咩事<br />\n<br />\n勉強一齊無幸福咪搵第二個<br />\n無咩話原唔原諒</blockquote><br />\n好野好野<br />\n你老豆就禽獸咁屌厭一個屌第個<br />\n你就禽獸咁比啲甜頭你就搖頭擺尾咁say ok<br />\n真係有其父必有其子<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa961501ef2df075c102ac996f0e43485af6e752","tid":294022,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T09:54:13.000Z","msg":"支持老竇包二奶 如果老竇有咁多錢的話"},{"pid":"a2f965111fdcffdb37c7f613636e6f1c405d9d78","tid":294022,"uid":48310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T14:21:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拿 醒樓主一招 我依家去溝你老豆個二奶 拎佢錢happy俾你老豆綠帽戴 佢先知你媽好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後皆大歡喜 又可以幫你出氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但條件係我飛9個二奶後 你同me一齊ok?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n脷申：快點利用me 吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個二奶5張幾有糖尿<br />\n同已經俾左綠帽我老竇帶<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要個女人俾人唱佢食小鮮肉<br />\n老竇成身綠到發光"},{"pid":"bc8467c4b2abad6952d36b5ea22c2d110738d86d","tid":294022,"uid":48310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T14:24:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>離少少題<br />\n<br />\n老豆係以前做中港司機 一星期有幾晚番唔到黎<br />\n但番到黎真係對我地好好 (任何方面)<br />\n同正常溫馨家庭冇分別<br />\n<br />\n如果你知佢有二奶 你會點？</blockquote><br />\n如果佢對我地好好<br />\n我都可以扮無野<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁多年補習同生活費由媽媽俾<br />\n有事打俾佢都唔會有人聽<br />\n返到黎乜都唔講係到㩒電話<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似當住酒店咁"},{"pid":"a75b4298cf79feb37167fbb35251864756ec8df3","tid":294022,"uid":76470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T14:27:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小四父母離婚 <br />\n細個無乜感受 <br />\n大個左發現<br />\n原來已經造成左好大既心理創傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n例如呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自己都係同你一樣小四父母離婚<br />\n我就覺得自己睇野好極端， 只有啱同錯，黑同白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b34ad4f0158d6a78bbd505e38cc82558177b5fa","tid":294022,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T14:29:51.000Z","msg":"難聽講句 身為仔女 <br />\n<br />\n你冇必要干涉呢種事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你老母床上做死魚 你老豆會唔會同你投訴<br />\n你老母出去勾佬俾你老豆知道咗 會唔會同你呻？<br />\n<br />\n根本好多嘢係有原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45f2be133e7af5756ad2a8774b5d48db4838989c","tid":294022,"uid":33367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T14:30:33.000Z","msg":"有得揀？"},{"pid":"f29ab1444daa6c5e14cc00bdce586ff2e3b3aa76","tid":294022,"uid":48310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T14:31:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小四父母離婚 <br />\n細個無乜感受 <br />\n大個左發現<br />\n原來已經造成左好大既心理創傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n例如呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自己都係同你一樣小四父母離婚<br />\n我就覺得自己睇野好極端， 只有啱同錯，黑同白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係小學左右發生<br />\n我都有同感<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 哀莫大於心死<br />\n當你一次又一次咁去呃自己 <br />\n自己老竇會改過返屋企<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而事實係佢改完又鍾個頭落去<br />\n個心好難受"},{"pid":"30d2509fb2d06810587c879857242cd09478ed11","tid":294022,"uid":74315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T14:31:58.000Z","msg":"會<br />\n因為我老母好撚極品<br />\n佢頂到咁耐都算佢好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22dc5fcdf7efff19fe22a053c80acddf6a614b4b","tid":294022,"uid":4672,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T14:32:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會<br />\n因為我老母好撚極品<br />\n佢頂到咁耐都算佢好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n+1 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e83d3722971d26d8e978222490ac550ba16a9be","tid":294022,"uid":55637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T14:33:16.000Z","msg":"過來人身分表示過多三五七年就淡，最後我老母自己都搵第二個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d21fa0f1e9166799a1d894c7a845e0510f1b5290","tid":294022,"uid":48310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T14:34:42.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n我只係中間人 <br />\n係佢地個仔女做唔到乜野<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔通咁就代表佢可以出軌咩?"},{"pid":"ca8e3a995c2eea8847c4af88eb7b6f5329d1a1bb","tid":294022,"uid":74315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T14:35:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係<br />\n我只係中間人 <br />\n係佢地個仔女做唔到乜野<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔通咁就代表佢可以出軌咩?</blockquote><br />\n事出必有因"},{"pid":"ee6b9736e62e474e4f41dc612aaf2ef46358fbc8","tid":294022,"uid":48310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T14:37:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會<br />\n因為我老母好撚極品<br />\n佢頂到咁耐都算佢好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果係咁我都會好過d<br />\n個二奶老又老過我媽<br />\n又食煙飲酒打牌賭錢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我媽就正常家庭主婦<br />\n都唔知貪佢乜野"},{"pid":"0e9642484a098bb0f3a11216029e4c9ba6819693","tid":294022,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T14:39:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>會<br />\n因為我老母好撚極品<br />\n佢頂到咁耐都算佢好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果係咁我都會好過d<br />\n個二奶老又老過我媽<br />\n又食煙飲酒打牌賭錢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我媽就正常家庭主婦<br />\n都唔知貪佢乜野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你睇老母個角度 同你老豆睇老母個角度係唔同架<br />\n<br />\n你睇唔到黑人憎個面<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f4090467d795026ce1dc253b30bada399eea8a2","tid":294022,"uid":35193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T14:39:56.000Z","msg":"關我撚事咩 呢啲垃圾<br />\n最好就惹撚埋性病翻黎"},{"pid":"4b71d483207eb990d841c50ff665b42384c251e8","tid":294022,"uid":91185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T19:39:45.000Z","msg":"唔會，如果當冇事發生係對你阿媽唔住。<br />\n利申，就算佢呢刻死撚咗我唔會去葬禮，最好快撚啲死，同個女人一齊死"},{"pid":"e45ff944c5f0efe6fc15d09ed71a2df940d96699","tid":294022,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T19:49:46.000Z","msg":"唔會<br />\n包二奶包到成日唔返屋企，偷屋企錢畀嗰個女人，又喝我老母，包完一個又一個，賤格"},{"pid":"143fc740c4ea97f2348669dfad5844c61979858b","tid":294022,"uid":106363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T19:54:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一定唔會<br />\n<br />\n未必脫離父子關係<br />\n但一定唔會再尊重佢<br />\n當佢廢老看待</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />包之前其實係唔係好尊重佢先?"},{"pid":"49a03e72a78302964ee416e39c2f61d68b8e7dd5","tid":294022,"uid":50610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T20:09:14.000Z","msg":"唔會，但聽老母講聽佢算鳩數， 到佢老死就係解脫<br />\n<br />\n當初3歲老母拖住我夜晚11點去大陸捉姦，𠴱陣指門拍左成個鐘先開門， 路過嘅公安都問我媽咩事， 聽完冇理我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n捉到姦之後，我老母想要離婚嫌帶我走，但老豆話離婚得但唔帶得我走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 心諗係愛自己自讓點解搞啲咁嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟著老母緊係話唔得啦，最後老母忍左佢，但冇原諒過老豆格硬一齊番，一路以來都覺得老豆老母之間冇愛，跟著老豆可能有種補償心態細個乜都會買俾我，但其實我讀小三𠴱陣已經明香𠴱陣發生咩事，佢啲補償狗都唔屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我到依家都係好錫我老母同好憎老豆，即使老母成日話我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17a19fc7d57071bfdbc9e98a8b909a710ca26c0b","tid":294022,"uid":67689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T20:15:24.000Z","msg":"絕對唔會！<br />\n當年我中一 我老豆為左包二包扔低左我地四兄弟同我呀媽 當時我只有12歲係屋企最細 而我呀媽為左供我地讀書 試過兩日做左38個鐘 日日做十幾個鐘 捱生捱死 為嘅只係想我地過得安安樂樂 而我個仆街老豆 足足七年都未試過出現返係我地眼前 毫無音訊<br />\n試問一個咁嘅男人 我可以點樣原諒？<br />\n媽媽我愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d214a37ca13a1c42e876712d94499a8b69c46c80","tid":294022,"uid":21629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T21:55:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>難聽講句 身為仔女 <br />\n<br />\n你冇必要干涉呢種事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你老母床上做死魚 你老豆會唔會同你投訴<br />\n你老母出去勾佬俾你老豆知道咗 會唔會同你呻？<br />\n<br />\n根本好多嘢係有原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有必要<br />\n如果係原因一 我會憎死我老豆<br />\n原因二嘅話 我老豆唔會食咁大隻死貓唔出聲 所以會怪老母<br />\n有原因又點 出軌根本唔值得原諒 因為有咗家庭有細路後 根本唔應該咁自私 而係要為細路著想<br />\n係咁自私就當初咪撚生"},{"pid":"a215993b6fba19bb4568d8bd2e2d3f7c1629e745","tid":294022,"uid":41137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T22:13:38.000Z","msg":"永遠唔會<br />\n<br />\n細個都係覺得無咩野<br />\n但大個就知自己無哂家座觀念同安全感就係因為佢<br />\n影響太多 就算自己明都彌補唔到"},{"pid":"bd727fee6858ce69f25102d403da6cfdcfd44bc1","tid":294022,"uid":124602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T13:15:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>永遠唔會<br />\n<br />\n細個都係覺得無咩野<br />\n但大個就知自己無哂家座觀念同安全感就係因為佢<br />\n影響太多 就算自己明都彌補唔到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同感"},{"pid":"6e2d33fd13150ee756308c46bc2fcdfee4e362bf","tid":294022,"uid":84951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T15:35:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2cd8b21610863e2502b109bc7bdd393ff6b74e3e","tid":294022,"uid":74315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T07:51:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>會<br />\n因為我老母好撚極品<br />\n佢頂到咁耐都算佢好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果係咁我都會好過d<br />\n個二奶老又老過我媽<br />\n又食煙飲酒打牌賭錢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我媽就正常家庭主婦<br />\n都唔知貪佢乜野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你睇老母個角度 同你老豆睇老母個角度係唔同架<br />\n<br />\n你睇唔到黑人憎個面<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n認同<br />\n如果個二奶條件咁差你老豆都中意<br />\n即係你老豆已經唔係貪後生靚女 而係個二奶有啲內在既野做得好過你老母<br />\n都不外乎係尊重 關心 體貼 呢啲"},{"pid":"e7aecd1e84efce2c5a6393588d8e3f69bb4ac6ae","tid":294022,"uid":93202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T08:10:03.000Z","msg":"我個仆街老母... 我絕對支持我老豆包二奶"},{"pid":"0369a982bfa444d1604f442f6c9acb0bcd369764","tid":294022,"uid":39428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T08:13:58.000Z","msg":"唔會<br />\n細個知道左之後就無尊重過條仆街"}]}